{"badges":["TM5","TM6"],"preparations":[{"content":["Place bread, onion and salt in mixing bowl then chop <b>Turbo\/2 sec\/2 times<b> until fine crumbs form. Transfer to a bowl and set aside.","Place 50 g butter in mixing bowl and heat <b>1 min\/90°C\/speed 1<b>.","Add mushrooms and chop <b>5 sec\/speed 5<b>. Scrape down sides of mixing bowl with spatula, then cook <b>5 min\/90°C\/speed 1<b>.","Add reserved breadcrumb mixture and stir <b>10 sec\/speed 3<b>, then scrape down sides of mixing bowl. Set mixing bowl aside and allow to cool for 15 minutes.","Add cream cheese, nutmeg, lemon juice, pepper and remaining 70 g butter then blend <b>20 sec\/speed 5<b>. Scrape down sides of mixing bowl and lid with spatula.","Add parsley, then blend again <b>20 sec\/speed 5<b>. Transfer to a bowl, cover with cling film and refrigerate for at least 1 hour before serving."]}],"ingredients":[{"title":"","content":["30 g bread, stale, roughly torn","20 g onion","½ - 1 tsp fine sea salt","120 g butter, soft","250 g fresh mushrooms (e.g. Chestnut or Portobello), quartered","100 g cream cheese","½ tsp freshly grated nutmeg","1 tsp lemon juice","½ tsp ground black pepper","3 sprigs fresh parsley"]}],"id":"r85235","imageLink":"https:\/\/1.bp.blogspot.com\/-buhb42PbzyE\/XZanAP1InjI\/AAAAAAAAg4o\/II7ndEvBcW8Jl7bgS8_Qhl3mf2tylN6mQCLcBGAsYHQ\/s1600\/0_-hAD1W0_Tmy18tln.png","title":"Mushroom Pâté","publishedAt":"2015-05-13T00:00:00Z","nutrition":{"protein":"2.6 g","fat":"33 g","uom":"per 100 gram","carbohydrates":"3.8 g","calories":"1350 kJ \/ 323 kcal"},"usefulItems":"cling film, refrigerator","basicInfo":["easy","15m","1h 30m","1 total recipe"]}